name: Chicken Factory Leakage
description:
Do your best not to die in the deadly chicken meat factory, that wants your precious meat! You have to jump dangerous bone saws and make sure not get pecked by the other irritated chickens. Do this while you progress through your last days of in a cage - one way or the other.

The game was made during Nordic Game Jam 2016.

Play the game in your browser at (doesn't support Google Chrome):
http://www.gamebucket.io/game/21fa89ac-11de-468d-a...
